title: Paranoid_Fisherman
---
<<if $fisherman_quest3_end is false>>
    <<if $fisherman_quest3_completed is false>>
        <<if $fisherman_quest3_active is false>>
            Fisherman: What's going on! What's going on!
            Fisherman: Help meeeee...
            Fisherman: Who are you?
            Fisherman: How did you get here?
        -> I live here?.
            Fisherman: Why should I believe you?
            -> Because I'm the lighthouse operator. I operate it every night.
                Fisherman: Phew...
                Fisherman: At least I can trust you.
                Fisherman: I've been going mad.
                Fisherman: Everyone is coming down with this disease.
                Fisherman: The locals call it "The Corruption".
                Fisher: DO YOU HAVE IT!?
                -> No, of course not.
                    <<if $eyeball_quest_active is false>>
                        Fisherman: Ok then, I believe you...
                    <<else>>
                        <<wait 1>>
                        Eyeball: You Will..
                        Eyeball: Sacrificeeeee Himmmm...
                        <<wait 1>>
                    <<endif>>
                    Fisherman: Now, why am I here...
                    Fisherman: I-I, need fuel.
                    Fisherman: Do you have any.
                    -> Yes, I'll grab it for you now.
                        Fisherman: Th-Thanks...
                        <<if $eyeball_quest_active is false>>
                            <<set $fisherman_quest3_active to true>>
                        <<else>>
                            <<set $fisherman_quest3_active to true>>
                            <<wait  2>>
                            Eyeball: Claim The Dagger...
                            Eyeball: Impaled Into Me...
                            Eyeball: And Sacrifice Him...
                        <<endif>>
                    -> No, I don't have any.
                        Fisherman: Oh...
                        Fisherman: I'm not sure if I can make it back.
                        <<set $corruption_level to $corruption_level + 1>>
                        <<set $fisherman_quest3_denied to true>>
                        <<set $fisherman_quest3_end to true>>
                -> Yes
                    Fisherman: YOU'RE DEAD!
                    <<set $murdered_ending to true>>
                    <<set $fisherman_quest3_end to true>>
        <<else>>
            Fisherman: Just waiting...   
        <<endif>>
    <<else>>
        Fisherman: Th-Thanks...
        Fisherman: I'll go now. Bye.
        <<set $fisherman_quest3_end to true>>
    <<endif>>
<<endif>>   
===
